title: Gorgeous Landscaping, 3 Pools, Central A/C, and more!
posting_body: ['Welcome to Pleasanton Glen Apartment Homes!', 'Like walking outdoors?', 'No problem!', 'Kottinger Village Park, a lovely manicured 4-acre park, is directly across the street from our Pleasanton, CA apartments.', '- Three sparkling pools with sun decks', '- Relaxing covered spa', '- Outdoor lounge area', '- Fully equipped fitness center', '- Beautiful courtyards with mature landscaping', '- Assigned covered parking', '- Extra rentable storage on-site', '- 24-hour laundry center', '- On-site friendly and professional management and maintenance team', '- Blocks from historical Downtown', '- Easy access to Bart, ACE Train, I-680 and I-580', '- Near major Tri-Valley employment centers, shopping, dining & entertainment', '- Award winning Pleasanton school district', '- 24-Hour parcel locker room', '- Many options to pay rent including, credit card, on-line and ACH', '- Resident referral program', '- Ice maker', '- Full kitchen Whirlpool stainless steel appliance package', '- Granite countertops in kitchen & bathrooms', '- Heat and AC', '- Designer window coverings', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Pricing is subject to change.', 'Call for details.']
